---
---
<section id="top" class="relative overflow-hidden pt-40 pb-32 sm:pt-48 sm:pb-40">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-bg opacity-40 [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,black_30%,transparent_75%)]"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-1/3 -z-10 mx-auto h-[40rem] w-[40rem] rounded-full bg-mint/[0.08] blur-[120px]"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-wide px-6 sm:px-10">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-8" data-reveal>
      <span class="text-mint">●</span>
      <span class="ml-2">Engineer · Founder · Co-founder, AgenticGrid Foundation</span>
    </p>

    <h1 class="display-h1 max-w-4xl" data-reveal style="transition-delay:80ms">
      Building the operating&nbsp;system
      <br class="hidden sm:block" />
      <span class="text-mint">for the energy transformation.</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="body-lg mt-10 max-w-narrow" data-reveal style="transition-delay:160ms">
      I'm Philip Beadle. I spent five years on the <a class="text-bone-50 underline decoration-mint/50 decoration-2 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-mint" href="https://www.holochain.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Holochain</a> core team building agent-centric protocols. In 2022 I was part of the team that started <a class="text-bone-50 underline decoration-mint/50 decoration-2 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-mint" href="https://ioen.tech" target="_blank" rel="noopener">IOEN</a> — the Internet of Energy Network — applying that thinking to grids. Today I lead <span class="text-bone-50">AgenticScale.ai</span> and its <span class="text-bone-50">AgenticGrid.ai</span> platform, shipping AI-powered simulations that let every stakeholder in the energy transformation work together.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4" data-reveal style="transition-delay:240ms">
      <a href="#thesis" class="pill">Read the thesis</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="pill-outline">Work with me</a>
    </div>

    <ol class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-2 gap-px overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-bone-400/10 bg-bone-400/10 lg:grid-cols-4" data-reveal-stagger>
      <li class="flex min-h-[12rem] flex-col bg-ink-900 p-8 transition-colors hover:bg-ink-800">
        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest text-mint">01</span>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-8">
          <p class="eyebrow">Tenure</p>
          <p class="mt-2 font-display text-2xl text-bone-50 sm:text-3xl">30 years</p>
          <p class="body mt-1 text-sm">Pro coding since the '90s</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex min-h-[12rem] flex-col bg-ink-900 p-8 transition-colors hover:bg-ink-800">
        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest text-mint">02</span>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-8">
          <p class="eyebrow">Holochain core</p>
          <p class="mt-2 font-display text-2xl text-bone-50 sm:text-3xl">5 years</p>
          <p class="body mt-1 text-sm">Agent-centric protocols</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex min-h-[12rem] flex-col bg-ink-900 p-8 transition-colors hover:bg-ink-800">
        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest text-mint">03</span>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-8">
          <p class="eyebrow">Microsoft MVP</p>
          <p class="mt-2 font-display text-2xl text-bone-50 sm:text-3xl">5 years</p>
          <p class="body mt-1 text-sm">Plus Wiley author</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex min-h-[12rem] flex-col bg-ink-900 p-8 transition-colors hover:bg-ink-800">
        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest text-mint">04</span>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-8">
          <p class="eyebrow">Now</p>
          <p class="mt-2 font-display text-2xl text-bone-50 sm:text-3xl">AgenticGrid</p>
          <p class="body mt-1 text-sm">RACE for 2030 project</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>
